^-|fp|1|CS||CP||fp||at|^C@2^y@3What I will review here is from Howard's 2 over 1 lessons from January 2008. I like the unrehearsed and direct nature of the live presentation. For additional information please visit his web site at |cp|1|AT|^*Hwww.bridgesights.com/hondobridge/#2over1^*N|CP||AT|. To fit my learning plan I have made minor modifications which are not substantive.|
