st||sk||rh||ah|OPENER'S REBID OPTIONS|ah|Quiz|ah|Board  4|sv|0|md|1sq7hakqj874dk9cjt,,|mb|1hp2dp?|lb|*BWhat bid would you make?^^3h|mb|3H|NT|
^b@2Bid ^*B3H^*N.  A jump rebid in your own suit after a two over one shows a solid suit AND suggests a slam.  The hand shown here is minimum for the 3H rebid.  You could have the CK too. |
