st||sk||rh||ah|OPENER'S REBID OPTIONS|ah|Quiz|ah|Board  5|sv|0|md|1sj8hakqj653dq8cqt,,|mb|1hp2dp|lb|*BWhat bid would you make?^^4h|mb|4h|NT|
^b@2Bid ^*B4H^*N.  Jumping to game shows a very specific kind of hand.  You are saying you have a solid trump suit but you don't have any other useful cards.  Partner is warned to proceed with caution. |
pg| ***** 230 ***** |


