%%%%%%%%%%%%%b6
st||sk||rh||ah|OPENER'S REBID OPTIONS|ah|Quiz|ah|Board  6|sv|0|md|1s7hakt73dq732ckq9,,|mb|1hp2dp|lb|*BWhat bid would you make?^^3s|mb|3s|NT|
^b@2Bid ^*B3S^*N.  Splinters can be used effectively after a two over one response.|
