%%%%%%%%%%%%%b7
st||sk||rh||ah|OPENER'S REBID OPTIONS|ah|Quiz|ah|Board  7|sv|0|md|1s73hkjt73cdackj652,,|mb|1hp2dp?|lb|*BWhat bid would you make?^^2h|mb|2h|NT|
^b@2Bid ^*B2H^*N.  Going to the three level to show clubs promises better values.  In the same way that a reverse to 2S would show a good hand, so too does a 3C bid.  The 3C bid, by the way, has an awkward but appropriate name.  It is called a ^*B'high level reverse'^*N.|
pg| ***** 234 ***** |


