You may say, as I did initially, "I bid slam once every 4th. of July so why should I spend my  money on a book on slam bidding?"  However, I considered it a bargain after what I learned from reading just three short chapters in the "Companion Workbook" which comes with the main book. The chapters were on hand evaluation, Splinters and Jacoby 2NT. Now, first an explanation of the topic by Howard. |
